#### Step C.3 — Evaluation metrics (bonus for report)

Compute **Precision@K**: Out of the top-K results, how many are truly relevant?

```python
def precision_at_k(recommended: list, relevant_job_families: list[str], k: int = 10) -> float:
    """What % of top-K recommendations match expected job families?"""
    hits = sum(1 for r in recommended[:k] if r["job_family"] in relevant_job_families)
    return hits / k
```

